description: Please join us for a special roundtable on Thursday, May 11th at 8 AM NYC (UTC-4) / 2 PM Montenegro / 9 PM Tokyo (UTC+11), where we will discuss the unique case of DAOs in Asia and what needs to be done in order to best support them.
